{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "事情发生在清理完魔兽回城的路上，\\nPANTHER和圣城的伙伴们\\n为了借宿而来到村子里的时候——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的男子",
            "context": "啊……不好了……\\n今后要怎么办才好……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "村民们看起来忧心忡忡……\\n是出什么事了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的男子",
            "context": "咦？你们这些人……很面生呢。\\n是过路的旅人吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "嗯。我们本打算\\n来这里借宿……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "但看来很不是时候呢。\\n这里到底发生了什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的男子",
            "context": "是龙……村子附近的那头龙，\\n突然来到这里……\\n要求我们献出活祭……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "龙要求的！？\\n可是龙不是人类的朋友吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "在圣城见到过的那些龙，\\n根本不会要求活祭……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "龙也有好有坏……\\n不是所有的龙\\n都会对人类很友好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "可是……如果是这样，和龙对话，\\n让他停止要求献祭不就好了？\\n龙又不是不懂人话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的男子",
            "context": "要、要是那样做，\\n惹龙不高兴了怎么办！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "龙会发火……\\n搞破坏什么的吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "不是的，PANTHER。\\n这个世界的人……\\n尤其是我们人类都很崇敬龙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "龙司掌魔力与自然，是特别的存在。\\n无论是天灾还是大自然的恩惠，\\n都是龙带来的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的男子",
            "context": "就是这样……要是没有龙，\\n土地将变得一片荒芜，\\n河水也会浑浊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的男子",
            "context": "我们人类只能顺从龙，\\n活下去……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "怎么会……就是说只能忍耐？\\n就算因为龙而遭遇不幸……\\n也只能认命吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "没错……在这个世界里\\n这就像是规矩一样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "这个世界的规矩……\\n必须遵守的规矩……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（既然如此，也许\\n我这个外人不该插嘴……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（可是……这样，真的好吗？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "嗯？那两个人，\\n是怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的少女",
            "context": "我替你去当活祭！\\n所以你一定要活下去！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女的朋友",
            "context": "不、不可以！\\n我才是被选为活祭的人！\\n你没必要去当活祭……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的少女",
            "context": "可是……我做不到！\\n我不能眼睁睁地\\n看着朋友成为活祭！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（那两个人……\\n和当初的我们一样……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（那时，我为了志帆……\\n而志帆也为了我……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（觉得为了救朋友，\\n牺牲自己也无所谓……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "我决定了！我果然还是\\n不能忍受！我要去和龙说，\\n让龙停止要求献祭！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉丝，你阻止我也没用！\\n卢卡！我一个人也可以……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不……我不会阻止你。\\n我也和你一起去！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "诶？可是……\\n这不是这个世界的规矩吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "嘿嘿！因为对我来说\\n打破规矩是家常便饭啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "我正好也想和这里的龙谈一谈！\\n所以我们一起去吧，PANTHER！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "喂、喂，你们两个……\\n真没辙……我也一起去吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "你们两个想乱来的时候，\\n要是没一个阻止的人\\n还不知道会出什么不得了的事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "卢卡！埃尔菲莉丝！\\n谢谢你们！太可靠了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喂！龙！你在的吧？\\n快点出来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（哇！这头龙怎么看起来\\n就很恐怖！？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（可、可是！我不能退缩。\\n一定要狠狠地教训教训他！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "那、那个……\\n我们有话要和你说！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210011_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斯特利伯格",
            "context": "嗯……有话要对我说吗？\\n好，欢迎你们的到来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "诶？\\n没想到还挺绅士的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊……他说要献出活祭，\\n还以为是个粗鲁的家伙……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210011_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斯特利伯格",
            "context": "活祭？你们在说什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "不、不是你在村里\\n这么说的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210011_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斯特利伯格",
            "context": "我的确是去了村里，\\n但没说过这种话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "原来如此……就是说，\\n村子里的人都误会了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210011_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斯特利伯格",
            "context": "嗯。我自远古以来\\n就在这个洞窟里闭关沉思……\\n但前阵子我突然想到一个主意。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210011_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斯特利伯格",
            "context": "我本是个异类……\\n所以也许能通过和人类对话\\n提升思想的高度。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "于是你说想有一个能聊天的人，\\n但村民们却误会了，\\n以为你要求献上活祭……对吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "村里那些人真是的……\\n一场误会弄得鸡飞狗跳。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "啊哈哈……他们一定是\\n吓了一跳，陷入恐慌了吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（我一开始也是这样……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "嗯？怎么了，PANTHER？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "没、没什么！我们还是\\n快点回到村里解开误会吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的男子",
            "context": "来、来了！龙来了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女的朋友",
            "context": "啊……这么快就……\\n但是，我必须得去当活祭！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的少女",
            "context": "这怎么行……不行！\\n还是我去当活祭！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "大家等一下！这都是误会！\\n其实根本不需要什么活祭！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊！\\n都是你们误会了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的男子",
            "context": "什、什么？\\n这话是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "呼……\\n误会解开了就好……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "嗯。村民们在我们的呼吁之下\\n终于冷静下来，肯听龙解释了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210011_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斯特利伯格",
            "context": "你们帮了我。多亏有你们\\n我才能顺利地和村民们对话。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210011_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "斯特利伯格",
            "context": "他们还和我约定，\\n轮番来和我聊天……\\n真的非常感谢你们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "不客气。\\n太好了呢，斯特利伯格。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "还有……你们两个也是。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120056_01",
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的少女",
            "context": "呜呜……呜，太好了……\\n真是太好了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少女的朋友",
            "context": "嗯！我们……有更多时间\\n能一直……在一起了呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（和好朋友共度的\\n充满欢笑的快乐时光……\\n是最为珍贵的宝物。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "PANTHER",
            "context": "（对吧？志帆……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}